Package model.entities.movableEntity

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bug
    Represents the bug in the game.
    Commit
    Represents a "Commit" item in the game.
    FlashDrive
    Represents a flash drive item in the game.
    Item
    Represents the items and stores the logic of how the players can pick up/interact with the items in the game
    Laptop
    Represent the characters in the game that will be found in the office section, and will have laptops with them that the player can clone code off.
    LaptopItem
    Represents an item in the game that can be "cloned" (stored) in a laptop (the player's inventory).
    MovableEntity
    This class represents a movable entity in the game.
    NonPlayerCharacters
    Represent a non player character in the game (characters that are not controlled by players but can be interacted with by the players in a set way).
    Player
    Represents a player in the game.
    ReadMe
    Represents a README file in the game ( a tablet that can be found laying around the office).
    SwipeCard
    Represents swipe card in the game and handles the game logic that is related to the player interacting with the swipe card (to pick it up or use it to unlock doors)
